Interface RiskAssessmentErrorCollector

    Used to collect errors during risk assessment.

      • getLocationLevelErrors

      • getRequestLevelErrors

        java.util.Map<OutboundPeriodRiskAssessmentTempStore,java.util.Set<RiskAssessmentError>> getRequestLevelErrors()
        Request level errors are sent from the risk assessment service if the entire request cannot be processed These errors are associated with each location temp store that was associated with the request
        Returns:
        all request level errors with every location temp store in the request
